title: Munchkin Love A Bowls Toddler & Baby with Lids, Bright Plastic Feeding Food Storage Containers, Dishwasher Safe Bowls, Weaning Spoons - 4 Pack (Multi Colour)
features: MUNCHKIN BABY FOOD BOWL SET: Set of 4 plastic toddler and baby feeding bowls with lids plus 2 x soft tip baby weaning spoons - perfect for breakfast, lunch, dinner and snack time, at home or away
100% SPILL-PROOF 100% LEAK-PROOF: The Munchkin bowls are deep with high sides for easy scooping, and seal shut with the included lids. The set's small plastic bowls are ideal as baby weaning bowls
EASY CARE BABY FEEDING SET: These durable, stackable baby dishes are top rack dishwasher safe, BPA-free and microwave safe. With easy grip sides they're great for picnics, nursery or travel

ALL YOU NEED FOR ON THE GO: The children's' bowls double as storage pots, for serving and storing food. The strong plastic snack bowls and baby spoons are ideal for infants and toddlers from 4+ months
DISCOVER THE MUNCHKIN BABY FOOD SETS: Complete your baby weaning set with the Munchkin infant feeding and dinnerware range for babies and toddlers, with suction bowls, toddler plates and sippy cups
description: Product Description When babies graduate from bottles to solids, it seems like there are never enough bowls to accommodate their needs - or contain the messes and leaks! Until now. This set of four interchangeable toddler bowls come with four lids and two soft-tip baby food spoons, making it the perfect baby food set for weaning. Great for baby food to toddler snacks, these bowls are easy to store and easy to take on the go. Plus, they stack neatly in the cupboard for easy storage. Stack up and stock up on this bright feeding set - the bowls and spoons are sure to earn a permanent place in your kitchen. • Munchkin 4 Baby Bowl and 2 Spoon Set • 4 colourful baby bowls with 4 lids and 2 baby feeding spoons • Spill-proof, leak-proof • Deep with high sides • Stackable for easy storage • Top-rack dishwasher-safe, BPA-free and microwave-safe • 4+ months • Ideal for baby led weaning or older children • Colours may vary • Not single-use plastic: please re-use It's the little things: Munchkin are an award-winning baby brand. Discover our baby products and toddler accessories, including baby weaning products, sippy cups, bath toys, stair gates, bouncers and more, all designed with little ones in mind. Safety Warning For your child's safety and health. Warning! Always use this product with adult supervision. Before each use, inspect the product. Throw away at the first sign of damage or weakness. Always check food temperature before feeding. Before first use, clean the product. Do not boil or steam sterilise. Do not use abrasive cleaning agents. Do not expose in direct sunlight. Do not let child walk or run while carrying the product. Top rack dishwasher safe. Please read and retain this information for future reference. Remove all packaging components before use. Not suitable for grill, oven or hob. Box Contains 4 x Bowls See more
